    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <p><b>As a</b> system<br/>
<b>I want</b> in‑store MTO orders to skip slot logic<br/>
<b>So that</b> they are fulfilled per store scheduling</p>
<h4><a name="AcceptanceCriteria"></a>Acceptance Criteria</h4>
<ul>
	<li>No slot selection required</li>
	<li>No slot validation triggered</li>
	<li>No FAS/Payments required</li>
	<li>Order submission succeeds without slot and payment data</li>
</ul>

            <br/>
        </td>
    </tr>
